originalSql:
SELECT 
    CONCAT('Part Name: ', p.p_name, ', Brand: ', p.p_brand, ', Type: ', p.p_type, 
           ', Container: ', p.p_container, ', Comment: ', p.p_comment) AS part_details,
    s.s_name AS supplier_name,
    CONCAT(c.c_name, ' (', c.c_address, ')') AS customer_info,
    o.o_orderkey,
    o.o_orderdate,
    SUM(l.l_extendedprice * (1 - l.l_discount)) AS total_revenue
FROM 
    part p
JOIN 
    partsupp ps ON p.p_partkey = ps.ps_partkey
JOIN 
    supplier s ON ps.ps_suppkey = s.s_suppkey
JOIN 
    lineitem l ON p.p_partkey = l.l_partkey
JOIN 
    orders o ON l.l_orderkey = o.o_orderkey
JOIN 
    customer c ON o.o_custkey = c.c_custkey
WHERE 
    p.p_retailprice > 100.00 
    AND o.o_orderdate BETWEEN '1997-01-01' AND '1997-12-31'
GROUP BY 
    p.p_name, p.p_brand, p.p_type, p.p_container, p.p_comment, s.s_name, 
    c.c_name, c.c_address, o.o_orderkey, o.o_orderdate
HAVING 
    SUM(l.l_extendedprice * (1 - l.l_discount)) > 5000.00
ORDER BY 
    total_revenue DESC

SELECT COALESCE("t5"."PART_DETAILS", "t5"."PART_DETAILS") AS "PART_DETAILS", "t5"."SUPPLIER_NAME", "t5"."CUSTOMER_INFO", "t5"."O_ORDERKEY", "t5"."O_ORDERDATE", "t5"."TOTAL_REVENUE"
FROM (SELECT MIN(CONCAT('Part Name: ', "part"."p_name", ', Brand: ', "part"."p_brand", ', Type: ', "part"."p_type", ', Container: ', "part"."p_container", ', Comment: ', "part"."p_comment")) AS "PART_DETAILS", MIN("supplier"."s_name") AS "SUPPLIER_NAME", MIN(CONCAT("customer"."c_name", ' (', "customer"."c_address", ')')) AS "CUSTOMER_INFO", "orders"."o_orderkey" AS "O_ORDERKEY", "orders"."o_orderdate" AS "O_ORDERDATE", SUM("lineitem"."l_extendedprice" * (1 - "lineitem"."l_discount")) AS "TOTAL_REVENUE"
FROM "part"
INNER JOIN "s1" ON "part"."p_partkey" = "s1"."ps_partkey"
INNER JOIN "supplier" ON "s1"."ps_suppkey" = "supplier"."s_suppkey"
INNER JOIN "lineitem" ON "part"."p_partkey" = "lineitem"."l_partkey"
INNER JOIN "orders" ON "lineitem"."l_orderkey" = "orders"."o_orderkey"
INNER JOIN "customer" ON "orders"."o_custkey" = "customer"."c_custkey"
WHERE "part"."p_retailprice" > 100.00 AND "orders"."o_orderdate" >= '1997-01-01' AND "orders"."o_orderdate" <= '1997-12-31'
GROUP BY "part"."p_name", "part"."p_brand", "part"."p_type", "part"."p_container", "part"."p_comment", "supplier"."s_name", "customer"."c_name", "customer"."c_address", "orders"."o_orderkey", "orders"."o_orderdate"
HAVING SUM("lineitem"."l_extendedprice" * (1 - "lineitem"."l_discount")) > 5000.0000
ORDER BY 6 DESC NULLS FIRST) AS "t5"
